        "timestamp": "2021-05-11 09:51:09.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nCouple of comments on this merge:\n\nI am aware this looks like a lot. \nBut it is to merge the msgrtr repo into the messageService repo, and combine them as one.\n\nThere is alot of pre-existing technical debt in the msgrtr repo, and will have to be actioned at some point.\nHowever, this story consisted of merging the repos and maintaining functionality. \n\nThe csits run successfully against this change, however, the CSITs do not cover the whole code base.\n\nAll the unit tests pass successfully. But again, I am reluctant to depend on them due to the aforementioned technical debt (due to previously commented out tests, and other deficiencies I noticed while merging)",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
